{"tid":1964780,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（求解答）朋友同我拗紋身屬唔屬於美容行業","createTime":"2020-04-09T05:12:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T05:24:50.000Z","uid":9711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7fd5452094b2de6a14cc40433189e698e166a30f","tid":1964780,"uid":9711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T05:12:57.000Z","msg":"朋友話最新美容院禁令包括埋紋身行業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我上網睇 政府刊憲提都冇提到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實關咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82ef97891d299a6a92efc00fc29181d8e5ecdf05","tid":1964780,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T05:16:57.000Z","msg":"Cap. 599F, Schedule 2, Part 2 <br />\n<br />\n<strong>美容院</strong> (beauty parlour) 指提供一項或多於一項以下類型服務所在的處所 &mdash;&mdash; <br />\n<br />\n(a)為美容目的而對身體任何部位(頭部毛髪除外)進行的化學、機械或發放能量的程序，包括為非醫學目的而進行的、涉及穿刺皮膚的美容程序； <br />\n<br />\n(b)美甲服務(包括修手甲或修腳甲服務、駁甲、塗甲油及藝術美甲)； <br />\n<br />\n(c)為非醫學目的而進行的改善脫髪服務(包括植髪及織髪)。"},{"pid":"746745aa4377d6519a2743073ae19f5fa4c12c98","tid":1964780,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82ef97891d299a6a92efc00fc29181d8e5ecdf05","tid":1964780,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T05:16:57.000Z","msg":"Cap. 599F, Schedule 2, Part 2 <br />\n<br />\n<strong>美容院</strong> (beauty parlour) 指提供一項或多於一項以下類型服務所在的處所 &mdash;&mdash; <br />\n<br />\n(a)為美容目的而對身體任何部位(頭部毛髪除外)進行的化學、機械或發放能量的程序，包括為非醫學目的而進行的、涉及穿刺皮膚的美容程序； <br />\n<br />\n(b)美甲服務(包括修手甲或修腳甲服務、駁甲、塗甲油及藝術美甲)； <br />\n<br />\n(c)為非醫學目的而進行的改善脫髪服務(包括植髪及織髪)。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T05:18:20.000Z","msg":"個規例好似有包紋身<im